[[!meta title="Tails 0.17.1 is out"]]
[[!tag announce]]

Tails, The Amnesic Incognito Live System, version 0.17.1, is out.

All users must upgrade as soon as possible.

[[!toc levels=1]]

# Changes

Notable user-visible changes include:

* Iceweasel
  - Upgrade to Iceweasel 17.0.4esr-0+tails1~bpo60+1.

* Hardware support
  - Update Linux to 3.2.39-2, that 
    It includes better support for graphics adapter, backported from
    Linux 3.4.29.
  - Temporarily drop the Rendition display driver.

* Bugfixes
  - Remove Indymedia IRC account, until we ship a version of Pidgin
    with SASL support.

See the online
Changelog
for technical details.

# Known issue

The VirtualBox support in Tails 0.17.1 is not as good as it could be.

